OL,3,CIrish government to cut excise duty on
OL,4,Cdiesel and petrol to help volatile
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FThe Irish Government is to cut excise
OL,8,Fduty on petrol and diesel to help
OL,9,Fpeople with volatile fuel prices.
OL,11,FThe proposals were agreed at a
OL,12,Fleaders' meeting on Monday evening and
OL,13,Fwill be brought to Cabinet on Tuesday
OL,14,Ffor approval.
OL,16,FThe Irish Government will cut excise
OL,17,Fduty on diesel by 20 cent and petrol
OL,18,Fby 15 cent from midnight on Wednesday
OL,19,Funtil the end of May.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
