OL,3,CIrish government to cut excise duty on
OL,4,Cdiesel and petrol to help volatile
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FA diesel rebate scheme for hauliers
OL,8,Fand bus operators is also expected,
OL,9,Fwhich will be backdated.
OL,11,FThe Fuel Allowance, a payment of 38
OL,12,Feuro a week to help with heating costs
OL,13,Ffrom late September until April, is
OL,14,Falso to be extended as part of a
OL,15,Fpackage of targeted measures to be
OL,16,Fannounced on Tuesday.
OL,18,FThe Irish Government has been pressed
OL,19,Fto intervene on soaring fuel costs
OL,20,Fsparked by the conflict between Iran
OL,21,Fand the US and Israel.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/3
